Package: jpcity
Type: Package
Title: Read and Convert Japanese Municipality Codes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: Read Japanese city codes to get city and prefecture names, or 
    convert to city codes at different points in time. In addition, it merges or
    splits wards of designated cities and gets all city codes at a specific 
    point in time.
